.Dd January 24, 2008
.Dt PUC 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm puc
.Nd PCI
.Dq Universal
Communications driver
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "device pci"
.Cd "device puc"
.Cd "device uart"
.Cd "device ppc"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
This driver acts as a shim to connect PCI serial and parallel ports to the
.Xr uart 4
and
.Xr ppc 4
driver.
.Pp
The list of supported devices is in
.Pa sys/dev/puc/pucdata.c .
Support for new cards should be added there.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr ppc 4 ,
.Xr uart 4
.Sh HISTORY
This driver took the idea from the
.Nx
.Nm
driver.
